# UX-first polish

After building or changing UI, do a quick first-time-user pass:

- **Visual hierarchy** — primary action/content first (e.g. swipe card before filters/search).
- **Defaults** — optional fields collapsed; auto-name when empty; allow save with sensible empty states.
- **Less clutter** — horizontal chips for filters; one labeled section instead of scattered controls.
- **Copy** — short hints at decision points (save with zero picks, rename vs add name).

Fix obvious friction in the same task. Do not add features outside YOURSTRAT_BUILD.md.
